			<change xml:lang="EN">
				<p sameAs="title">Information letter from João da Costa, a clerk, to Manuel Rodrigues de Melo, a judge.</p>
				<p sameAs="summary">The author explains that a highwayman that was arrested has been recognized by two witnesses who swore  in secret for fear of  a violent payback.</p>
				<p sameAs="settingDesc">Jerónimo de Morais, Manuel de Jesus dos Passos (or Estêvão da Assunção Longo) and José de Sousa were prosecuted for being highwaymen and robbers and for traveling with fake names on their passports.</p>
				<p sameAs="text"></p></change>
		</revisionDesc>
